{
  "stem": "4753.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I came to middle of the village.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then a railroad man came, and talked to the lady, told her that the train left for Sweden.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So she got very scared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I said, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I am sure other, other train will come.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I am going to the railroad station, and I will wait there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we parted, with the two bag of bread, and the bottle of milk, what she gave me, in my chest.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When I came to the middle of the empty space between the railroad and the village, there was a white van on the road, stopped.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then a nun, or nurse, with the white outfit, came out from the van.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Later, I realized that was a Red Cross van.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she was telling me that two other girls who run after me is inside in the car, and crying.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she doesn't know what to do with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I should come and sit in the car, because the train left.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I did go into the van, and I told the two girls-- said, why you are crying?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I felt right away free.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Matter of fact, I never felt like an inmate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the strangest things for me to think about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was beaten many times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we came to a hospital, where they cleaned us, and gave us beautiful, clean underwear, and a set of clothes, and put us in a hospital bedroom, with several beds [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were-- each one of us had a bed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The two other girls got on the floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She said, that's too comfortable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I loved my bed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, the nurses were wonderful.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
